title: MixTape Calculator [1.0.0] Android App
description:
MixTape Calculator is the perfect tool to create your mix tapes!
  
Easily figure out what songs you can fit on each side of the cassette,
either sequentially or with the best possible fit (i.e. add as many as possible!).
  
The MixTape Calculator also calculates the Tape fill taking into account the song
gap you choose. Just add songs and their length to the list and press "Calculate".

MixTape Calculator will automatically give you the Tape space usage statistics,
so you can optimize your cassette.

Use the MixTape Calculator to eliminate those annoying "empty spaces" and "cut songs"
to create the perfect listening experience.
  
Features:
- Easy to use!
- Tape length selection.
- Best Fit: As many as possible.
- Sequential: No cut songs.
- Gap between songs (silence).
- Space usage statistics.
  
  
Now it's easy to create perfect MixTapes!
  
  
Install
ENJOY
